{"TopicId":83776,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"I\u0026#039;ve made a lasers puzzle game: Luminoso","CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-04T10:25:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-04T10:25:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo I\u0027m currently developing a lasers puzzle game called Luminoso. I\u0027m pretty sure you all know some variants of the concept.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s currently on \u003Ca href=\u0022http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=309533045\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESteam Greenlight\u003C/a\u003E, so if you like the concept, I wouldn\u0027t mind your vote \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF0000;\u0022\u003EEdit: \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://store.steampowered.com/app/364660\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF0000;\u0022\u003ENow available\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF0000;\u0022\u003E on Steam.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=309533045\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://luminoso.blizzy.de/img/screenshots/screenshot-04_thumb.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot-04_thumb.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe level editor is now available for download. I don\u0027t think I can link the download here, however, as I don\u0027t want to open up the source code as per the forum rules. You can find it in the Steam announcements.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBy the way, the game also has a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.facebook.com/luminosogame\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EFacebook page\u003C/a\u003E, if you\u0027re so inclined.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-17T18:35:27Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2015 06:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by blizzy78\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wanderfound","CreatedById":112611,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-04T10:52:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYup.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHave you seen Khet? Non-virtual laser chess. Very good game; simple rules, but chess-like strategic depth.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.khet.com\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.khet.com\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-06T16:37:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGood news, everyone: The level editor is now available for download. I don\u0027t think I can link the download here, however, as I don\u0027t want to open up the source code as per the forum rules.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Javster","CreatedById":74613,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-07T20:01:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks fun. I\u0027ll vote yes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-20T13:52:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust in case anyone is interested, I\u0027ve submitted Luminoso to Apple\u0027s app store as well. It\u0027s still sitting in the waiting queue, however.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-23T20:56:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWohoo, it is now \u003Ca href=\u0022https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/luminoso/id976962291?mt=8\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eavailable\u003C/a\u003E on the App Store as well \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gmpd2000","CreatedById":37101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-23T21:16:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat\u0027ll be the purchase price? Considering to buy it once it comes out.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-23T21:18:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s currently $2.99/EUR 2.99.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T20:30:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWohoo, Luminoso just got greenlit on Steam!\u003C/strong\u003E You read it here first!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENow I guess I have to do some paperwork and send it to Valve before it can actually go live.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEdit: This seems to be easier than I thought. Currently in the process of setting up the store page.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEdit 2: All set up, now it\u0027s up to Valve to do a review of my settings. Once that\u0027s done, it should go live soon.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-17T00:42:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2015 12:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by blizzy78\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T18:36:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAnd \u003Ca href=\u0022http://store.steampowered.com/app/364660\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ewe are live\u003C/a\u003E now! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizzle","CreatedById":31588,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T22:54:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt looks good, but $9 is really steep.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tommygun","CreatedById":41293,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-18T01:45:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis kind of reminds me of some of those ladder logic simulators for industrial PLC.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}